  "obverse": {
    "description": "Country name on top, symbolic effigy of the Republic, interpreted in the form of sculpture.\r\nIn the lower right corner, a tactile mark with a slanted bar to the right, for use by the visually impaired. \r\nFace value in number on upper right, in number and letters on lower left.\r\n\r\nNombre del país arriba, imagen de la República, interpretada como escultura.\r\nAbajo, derecha marca táctil, barra inclinada a la derecha, para uso de discapacitados visuales.\r\nValor facial en número arriba derecha, en número y letras abajo izquierda.",
    "lettering": "REPÚBLICA FEDERATIVA DO BRASIL 2\r\n2010\r\n2\r\nREAIS\r\nREPÚBLICA\r\nDEUS SEJA LOUVADO",
    "lettering_scripts": [
      {
        "name": "Latin"
      }
    ],
    "lettering_translation": "Federative Republic of Brazil \r\n2\r\n2010\r\n2\r\nReais\r\nRepublic\r\nGod be praised\r\n\r\nRepública Federativa de Brasil    2\r\n2010\r\n2 Reais\r\nRepública\r\nDios sea alabado",
    "picture": "https://en.numista.com/catalogue/photos/bresil/5eb4b89f99c432.97713538-original.jpg",
    "thumbnail": "https://en.numista.com/catalogue/photos/bresil/5eb4b89f99c432.97713538-180.jpg",
    "picture_copyright": "SmoCa"
  },
  "reverse": {
    "description": "On the left, sea turtle (Eretmochelys imbricata) swimming; and on the right, two sea turtles swimming next to each other. In the background marine vegetation and starfish. Issuer name on top, face value in number on top left and right, in letters on lower right.\r\n\r\nA la izquierda, tortuga marina (Eretmochelys imbricata) nadando; y a la derecha dos tortugas nadando juntas. En el fondo, vegetación marina y estrella de mar. Nombre del emisor arriba, valor facial en número arriba a izquierda y derecha, en letras abajo derecha.",
    "lettering": "BANCO CENTRAL DO BRASIL 2\r\n2\r\nMINISTRO DA FAZENDA\r\nPRESIDENTE DO\r\nBANCO CENTRAL DO BRASIL\r\nTARTARUGA MARINHA\r\nDOIS REAIS\r\nCASA DA MOEDA DO BRASIL",
    "lettering_scripts": [
      {
        "name": "Latin"
      }
    ],
    "lettering_translation": "Central Bank of Brazil       2\r\n2\r\nFinance Minister\r\nPresident of the Central Bank of Brazil\r\nSea turtle\r\nTwo Reais\r\nCoin House of Brazil (Brazilian Mint)\r\n\r\nBanco Central de Brasil          2\r\n2\r\nMinistro de Finanzas\r\nPresidente del Banco Central de Brasil\r\nTortuga marina\r\nDos Reais\r\nCasa de la Moneda de Brasil (ceca)",
    "picture": "https://en.numista.com/catalogue/photos/bresil/5eb4b8a08cb728.23385429-original.jpg",
    "thumbnail": "https://en.numista.com/catalogue/photos/bresil/5eb4b8a08cb728.23385429-180.jpg",
    "picture_copyright": "SmoCa"
  },
