errer ugc\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sea_turtle\"><i>Tortuga marina (Eretmochelys imbricata)</i></a><br>---<br><strong>Notas</strong><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1d428e8152.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1d428e8152.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>more...</i> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.numista.com/numisdoc/brazil-179.html\">República Federativa de <strong>Brasil</strong></a> y <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer ugc\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Brazilian_real\">Real (R$)</a><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1d3e357398.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1d3e357398.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i><strong>Important:</strong> La fecha que figura es 2010, pero fue emitido en varios años (nueva serie de billetes)</i><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1c97f92669.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1c97f92669.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>Marca táctil para discapacitados visuales</i><br>---<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1c998235eb.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1c998235eb.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/5eb1c9a9f0acd.jpg\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/5eb1c9a9f0acd.jpg\" alt=\"\"></a><br><i>Espécimen</i><br><br>UV activity:<br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a028e8c2721.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a028e8c2721.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br><a href=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/64a028f989683.png\"><img src=\"https://en.numista.com/catalogue/images/miniatures/64a028f989683.png\" alt=\"\"></a><br>© gyoschak</p>",
